A collision in Tecoma Road in Astra Park, Kingsburgh, claimed the life of a tractor driver, recently.Netcare 99 responded to the scene and media liaison officer, Shawn Herbst said, “Reports from the scene indicated that a tractor and a car were involved in a collision resulting in the tractor overturning.Medics assessed the scene and found that the tractor driver had sustained fatal injuries and was sadly declared deceased.” Life Response 24/7 medics also attended the scene and paramedic Njabulo said the driver of the motor vehicle sustained mild injuries. According to Njabulo, the driver was stabilised on scene and transported to hospital for further medical care.